---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Callout from '../../components/Callout.astro';

const article = { author: "Maine Dispensary Guide Editorial Team", publishDate: "2026-01-15", modifiedDate: "2026-03-28", section: "City Guides" };
export const title = "Saco Dispensary Guide";
---

<Layout 
  title="Saco Maine Dispensary Guide" 
  description="Saco, Maine cannabis dispensary guide. 2026 market opportunities, strategic locations, local fee structures, and OCP investment requirements."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500916434205-0c77489c6cf7?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=400"
  article={article}
>
  <article>
    <div class="article-header">
      <h1>Saco Cannabis Guide</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Current status and alternatives for Saco, Maine</p>
    </div>

    <section class="fact-box">
      <h2>📋 Saco Status</h2>
      <table aria-label="Saco dispensary requirements and market data" caption="Key requirements and market data for opening a dispensary in Saco">
        <thead><tr><th scope="col">Requirement</th><th scope="col">Details</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><strong>Adult-Use Retail</strong></td><td>❌ NOT PERMITTED</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Medical Dispensary</strong></td><td>❌ Not currently permitted</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Nearby Options</strong></td><td>Portland, Biddeford, Old Orchard Beach</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Current Status</h2>
      <p>Saco has NOT opted into allowing adult-use cannabis retail operations. The city has restricted cannabis business licenses while evaluating the impact on the community. Under <a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/adult-use" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine OCP adult-use regulations</a>, municipalities must opt-in before retail licenses can be issued.</p>
    </section>

    <Callout title="Regulatory Reality" type="warning">
      Saco currently prohibits retail cannabis operations. This guide helps entrepreneurs understand current restrictions and identify alternative strategies.
    </Callout>

    <section>
      <h2>Nearby Opportunities</h2>
      <p>For entrepreneurs committed to the Saco market, alternative approaches include establishing a <a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-cultivation-guide/">cultivation facility</a>, operating a manufacturing operation, or launching a delivery service from a licensed location in a neighboring municipality. Cultivation licenses in Maine do not require municipal opt-in, making them a viable alternative to retail. Additionally, the York County region has shown growing interest in cannabis commerce, and Saco's restrictions may be revisited as neighboring communities establish successful operations.</p>
      <table aria-label="Saco nearby opportunities">
        <thead>
          <tr><th>City</th><th>Distance</th><th>Status</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Biddeford</td><td>3 miles</td><td>Open</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Old Orchard Beach</td><td>5 miles</td><td>Open</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Portland</td><td>10 miles</td><td>Open</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>⚠️ Closed:</strong> Retail cannabis not permitted</li>
        <li><strong>📍 Alternative:</strong> Consider Biddeford (3 miles)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>Verify current local ordinances before pursuing any cannabis business.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .article-header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2, section h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; color: #1a1a1a; }
  .fact-box { background: rgba(88, 129, 87, 0.1); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary); }
  .fact-box h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .fact-box table { margin: 0; }
</style>